== Installation ==

=== USE flags ===

{{USEflag|package=net-dialup/freeradius}}

=== Emerge ===

Install FreeRADIUS:

{{Emerge|net-dialup/freeradius}}

Start FreeRADIUS:

{{RootCmd|rc-service radiusd start}}

Add FreeRADIUS to the default runlevel:

{{RootCmd|rc-update add radiusd default}}

== Configuration ==

Configuration files are located in {{Path|/etc/raddb/}} directory.

For general configuration visit the [https://wiki.freeradius.org/guide/Basic-configuration-HOWTO Basic configuration HOWTO].

Further hints are listed in the [https://wiki.freeradius.org/guide/HOWTO FreeRADIUS HOWTO] wiki page.

